Death from putting puzzle box in plant
If you throw a heavy object at the vending machine to break it, Mitch will get impaled by the glass and bleed out.
If you use the rope on the vending machine, it will fall and crush Mitch.
If you use the rope on the clock, it will fall and crush Mitch.
Cut any wire that has electricity going through it.
Go through any area with moving wires in the basement. This will cause them to wrap around Mitch and eventually crush him to death.

Get caught in one of the writer’s traps. This will make her get up from her work and scream. She will sprint toward Mitch and cut off his feet with a broken paper cutter. The dead end picture has the writer furiously working still while Mitch’s brutalized corpse is held up by a mannequin base. His body is romantically dipping a mannequin dressed as Jackie.
If the Writer catches Mitch while she’s roaming (after her card is taken), she will bisect him with a single swipe of the paper cutter.

If you try to take the basement handle from the Doll without using a replacement, she will grab Mitch’s hand. He struggles and tries to get away, but she has a fucking death grip. Threads start to grow out of her hand and pierce Mitch’s skin. He screams, causing the other dolls to boo him for being so loud in a library. They say something about how someone should shove cotton in his mouth or some shit. The Dead End screen is of Mitch’s body overflowing with cotton, his eyes bloodshot, and strings holding him up. The dolls are surrounding him in a circle.
